Package: shlrtools
Title: Tools for the Simulation Hockey League
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: person("Canadice", "SHL", email = "canadice.shl@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Package provides functions and tools for the Simulation Hockey League. The package has functions for 
  scraping the forum website, analyzing saved games from FHM6/8, 
  visualization of data from the SHL Index and more.
